    "description": "Get the kids involved in the kitchen with this delicious Italian classic. You'll top crisp pizza base with a herby tomato sauce and creamy mozzarella before baking to perfection. Serve with a cucumber and rocket salad, a drizzle of chilli oil for the grown-ups and dough balls to the side.",
