    "cooking_instructions": [
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Preheat the oven to 200\u00b0C/ 180\u00b0C (fan)/ gas 6</p><p>Peel and grate your <strong>garlic</strong></p><p>Drain your <strong>mozzarella</strong>, then pat and squeeze as much liquid out as you can with kitchen paper</p><p>Tear the <strong>drained</strong> <strong>mozzarella</strong> into rough, bite-sized pieces</p>",
            "order": 1,
            "image": "/images/instructions/margherita-pizza-with-chilli-oil-and-salad-with-side/step-1.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Put a large baking tray (or two!) in the oven to heat up (this will stop the pizza bottom[s] from going soggy!)</p><p>Add your <strong>tomato</strong> <strong>paste</strong> to a bowl with the <strong>grated</strong> <strong>garlic</strong>, <strong>dried</strong> <strong>oregano</strong> and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong>, <strong>pepper</strong> and <strong>sugar</strong></p><p>Add 5 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[7 1/2 tbsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[10 tbsp]</span> <strong>cold</strong> <strong>water </strong>and stir it all together \u2013 this is your <strong>tomato</strong> <strong>base</strong></p>",
            "order": 2,
            "image": "/images/instructions/margherita-pizza-with-chilli-oil-and-salad-with-side/step-2.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Wash your <strong>salad</strong>,<strong> </strong>then pat it dry with kitchen paper</p><p>Cut your <strong>cucumber</strong> into batons</p><p>Combine your <strong>balsamic</strong> <strong>vinegar</strong> with a generous drizzle of <strong>olive</strong> <strong>oil</strong> in a bowl \u2013 this is your <strong>balsamic</strong> <strong>dressing</strong></p>",
            "order": 3,
            "image": "/images/instructions/margherita-pizza-with-chilli-oil-and-salad-with-side/step-3.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Remove the heated tray[s] from the oven and add your <strong>pizza</strong> <strong>base[s]</strong></p><p>Spread the <strong>tomato</strong> <strong>base</strong> evenly over your <strong>pizza</strong> <strong>base[s]</strong> with the back of a spoon</p><p>Top with the <strong>torn</strong> <strong>mozzarella</strong></p><p>Tip: Cooking for 2 or more? Make sure the pizza doesn't overlap on the tray to avoid raw dough!</p>",
            "order": 4,
            "image": "/images/instructions/margherita-pizza-with-chilli-oil-and-salad-with-side/step-4.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Put the tray[s] in the oven for 13-15 min or until the cheese has melted and the base is crisp \u2013 this is your <strong>margherita</strong> <strong>pizza</strong></p>",
            "order": 5,
            "image": "/images/instructions/margherita-pizza-with-chilli-oil-and-salad-with-side/step-5.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Whilst the pizza is cooking, heat a pot with a drizzle of<span class=\"text-danger\"> </span><strong>olive oil </strong>over a medium heat for 1-2 min or until very hot</p><p>Add your <strong>chilli flakes</strong> (can't handle the heat? Go easy!) to a small heatproof bowl with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong></p><p>Carefully pour the heated oil into the bowl, give it a good mix up and set aside for later \u2013 this is your <strong>chilli oil</strong></p>",
            "order": 6,
            "image": "/images/instructions/margherita-pizza-with-chilli-oil-and-salad-with-side/step-6.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Combine your <strong>salad</strong> and <strong>cucumber</strong> <strong>batons</strong> in a bowl with the <strong>balsamic</strong> <strong>dressing</strong></p><p><strong><span class=\"text-danger\">Tip: Cooking for kids? Set aside half of the cucumber batons for serving!</span></strong></p><p>Give everything a good mix up \u2013 this is your <strong>salad</strong></p>",
            "order": 7,
            "image": "/images/instructions/margherita-pizza-with-chilli-oil-and-salad-with-side/step-7.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>margherita</strong> <strong>pizza</strong> and drizzle over the <strong>chilli</strong> <strong>oil</strong> (not a fan of spice? Just add a little!)</p><p>Serve with the <strong>salad</strong> to the side</p><p><strong><span class=\"text-danger\">Tip: Cooking for kids? Leave off the chilli oil and serve the reserved cucumber batons to the side!</span></strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
            "order": 8
        }
    ],
